{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"nonisolated"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"tint"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"_"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"tint"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore5ColorV","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Color","text":"Color"},{"kind":"text","text":"?) -> "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"some"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View","text":"View"},{"kind":"text","text":"\n"}],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"tint","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The tint ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Color","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" to apply.","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Use this method to override the default accent color for this view.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Unlike an app’s accent color, which can be overridden by user","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"preference, the tint color is always respected and should be used as a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"way to provide additional meaning to the control.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This example shows Answer and Decline buttons with "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/ShapeStyle\/green"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":